Title: Back to Aggra
Description:
Return to the Horde Base Camp and let Aggra know that we still live, $n.

Tell her that I am moving on to the Wild Overlook and that we will all meet up on the northwest side of the island. I expect to see you there.

We will track down the Alliance and slay them to the last!
ObjectivesText: Inform Aggra at the Horde Base Camp on the Lost Isles of all that has transpired.
RewardText:
<Aggra gives you the eye as if she doesn't quite believe what you are telling her.>

I am not easily impressed, but if what you are telling me is true, then I have never before heard of such a thing.

You have my thanks, $n.
